question:
District category contains Institute District, Gated Community, and Research and Innovation Park.
Supermarkets category contains Eataly, Metro (Canada), and WinCo Foods.
Product category contains Canned Peas, Evaporated Milk, and Cheesecake.
Ingredient category contains Star Anise, Peanut Butter, and Flour.
The number of each Eataly 's Cheesecake equals each Gated Community 's Eataly.
The number of each Metro (Canada) 's Canned Peas equals each Institute District 's WinCo Foods.
The number of each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter equals 17.
The number of each Canned Peas 's Flour equals each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter.
The number of each Cheesecake 's Peanut Butter equals the sum of each Canned Peas 's Flour and each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter.
The number of each Institute District 's WinCo Foods equals 16 times each Gated Community 's Eataly.
The number of each Metro (Canada) 's Evaporated Milk equals each Canned Peas 's Star Anise.
The number of each Evaporated Milk 's Flour equals each Canned Peas 's Star Anise.
The number of each Eataly 's Canned Peas equals 20 times each Gated Community 's Eataly.
The number of each WinCo Foods 's Evaporated Milk equals 14 times the difference of each Eataly 's Canned Peas and each Institute District 's WinCo Foods.
The number of each Institute District 's Eataly equals 5 more than the sum of each Canned Peas 's Ingredient, each Metro (Canada) 's Evaporated Milk, and each Eataly 's Canned Peas.
The number of each Canned Peas 's Star Anise equals each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter.
The number of each WinCo Foods 's Canned Peas equals the sum of each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter, each Canned Peas 's Star Anise, each Cheesecake 's Peanut Butter, and each Cheesecake 's Ingredient.
The number of each Gated Community 's Eataly equals 5.
The number of each Research and Innovation Park 's Eataly equals each Gated Community 's Eataly.
How many Ingredient does Cheesecake have?
solution:
Define each Evaporated Milk 's Peanut Butter as Y; So Y = 17.
Define each Canned Peas 's Flour as t; So t = Y = 17.
Define each Cheesecake 's Peanut Butter as l; So l = t + Y = 17 + 17 = 11.
Define each Cheesecake 's Ingredient as Q; So Q = l = 11.
